    <string name="block_understand_title">A deal is a deal</string>
    <string name="block_understand_body">This block is not a hijack — it\'s the agreement you made. DollarBlock is not a virus, doesn\'t lock your phone and never forces you to pay: paying is just the shortcut for getting this app back today. You can close this screen and get on with your day, and you can disable monitoring for this app at any time in the Apps tab. We only charge what was agreed — nothing else.</string>

